$\triangle ABC\sim\triangle DBE$, $BC=20\text{ cm}.$ How many centimeters long is $DE$? Express your answer as a decimal to the nearest tenth. [asy]
draw((0,0)--(20,0)--(20,12)--cycle);
draw((13,0)--(13,7.8));
label("$B$",(0,0),SW);
label("$E$",(13,0),S);
